# Tender Announcement

## Procurement Specialist Level 2 for the Financial Consumer Agency of Canada (FCAC)

### Solicitation Number
* 20222841

### Closing Date
* 2023-04-25, at 14:00:00

### Description
The Financial Consumer Agency of Canada (FCAC) invites bids for the provision of a Procurement Specialist Level 2 consultant to support task-based professional services under the E60ZT-18TSPS Supply Arrangement.

### Key Dates
* Expected Contract Start Date: 2023-05-08
* Expected Contract End Date: 2024-03-31

### Trade Agreements
This tender is open to bidders from Canada and participating countries under the following trade agreements:

* Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA)
* World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)
* North American Free Trade Agreement (NAFTA)
* Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)
* Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
* Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)
* Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
* Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)

### Contact Information
For more information, please contact:

* Pavlo Kyryakov, FCAC.Contract-Contrat.ACFC@fcac-acfc.gc.ca, (613) 290-2003

### Tender Documents
The tender notice and supporting documents are available at:

* https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/4634/npp_20222841_eng.pdf (English)
